title: Facebook begins labeling, but not fact-checking, posts from Trump and Biden
text: After President Donald Trump posted an unfounded claim to Facebook (FB) on Tuesday that mail-in voting could lead to a "corrupt election," the social network slapped a label on it.

title: A significant part of tech growth is sustainable, says Goldman Sachs' Heath Terry
text: Heath Terry of Goldman Sachs joins "Squawk Alley" to discuss the tech sector as stocks see strong gains.

title: Facebook Chases Tiktok (Again) With a New Instagram Feature
text: The aging social media giant tries to recapture its youth by baking a TikTok-like feature into Instagram.

title: Big 5 US Tech Giants Hit $6.4 Trillion in Market Cap, a 53% Jump in a Year
text: The market capitalization of five U.S. technology giants rose from $4.1 trillion to $6.4 trillion in the 12 months between June 2019 and July 2020.

title: Facebook's Instagram rolls out new tool for personal fundraising
text: Instagram users in the US, UK and Ireland will be able to create fundraisers.
